<br>
Around 6 months later (late 99?), they added the IC quest, which produced no drop versions of the Astral and Frost runes (you still needed a high Research skill to combine them successfully), and the resulting scroll was also no drop.<br>
<br>
But that was in addition to the old way of getting it, which never went away.  Both methods still exist to this day, but I doubt that the quest is done much anymore. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/umorgail.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Morgail</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(2/12/02 11:23:03 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm8.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=244.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Added info</span><hr size=1> On Karana, my alliance took down Vox again and I was suprized to see the Spell: Ice Comet looted off the lizard.  Has this spell dropped off Vox before?  Maybe it will help maybe it won't but I thought it was strange.<br>
